142
00:08:18,519 --> 00:08:19,903
- Preboha!
- Hej!

143
00:08:21,480 --> 00:08:22,856
Krvácate!

144
00:08:22,857 --> 00:08:25,608
Počkajte, pozriem sa na to. Nie!

145
00:08:25,609 --> 00:08:27,277
