Ustúpte ľudia!

153
00:08:41,500 --> 00:08:42,959
- Rýchlo!
- Opatrne!

154
00:08:42,960 --> 00:08:44,919
Áno, je to strelná rana!

155
00:08:44,920 --> 00:08:47,473
Ihneď pošlite sanitku!

156
00:08:47,506 --> 00:08:49,340
Dajte ma dole. Dokážem chodiť. 

157
00:08:49,341 --> 00:08:50,758
Upokojte sa!

158
00:08:50,759 --> 00:08:52,978
Uhnite z cesty!

159
00:08:53,179 --> 00:08:54,888
Nevidíte, že je zranená?

160
00:08:54,889 --> 00:08:57,733
