207
00:11:34,631 --> 00:11:35,766
Som v pohode.

208
00:11:36,800 --> 00:11:38,468
Mali by ste ležať.

209
00:11:38,469 --> 00:11:40,687
- Budeme opatrní.
- Som v poriadku.

210
00:11:41,555 --> 00:11:43,148
Pomaly.

211
00:11:44,333 --> 00:11:46,351
<font color="#ffff00">CHA DAL-GEON OBVIŇUJE
PREZIDENTA</font>

212
00:11:46,352 --> 00:11:47,643
Inernet sa celkom zbláznil.

213
