486
00:36:58,120 --> 00:36:59,929
<font color="#ffff00">NAŠE DETI NÁS VOLAJÚ.</font>

487
00:36:59,930 --> 00:37:01,139
<font color="#ffff00">LEE PIL-YONG</font>

488
00:37:01,140 --> 00:37:02,474
<font color="#ffff00">CHCEME PRAVDU, 
